{"tid":53524,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"一句 Samsung Galaxy Note 7 令飛機幾乎要緊急降落","createTime":"2016-12-24T18:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T18:44:16.000Z","uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0517fb3191839f1a1891bd0e5f08f3c32d31dece","tid":53524,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:06:57.000Z","msg":"用手機開 Hotspot 同朋友開心 share Wifi 好正常，小編就見過有朋友設定佢個 Wifi (SSID) 做：有本事你就 Hack 我嚟用 (好有霸氣) / 每分鐘收費六毫之類&hellip;不過最近就有位乘搭美國內陸航班的乘客將佢個手機 Wifi 命名為「Samsung Galaxy Note7_1097」，仲差少少搞到航班要中途急降。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news/vincent/20161223_note7_scarethe-passengers01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews%2Fvincent%2F20161223_note7_scarethe-passengers01.jpg&h=6e86b4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有乘客 capture 當刻航班上搜尋到的 Wifi 網絡<br />\n<br />\n話說，一班由三藩市開往波士頓的航班上，機組人員嚇然發現於航班上搜尋到一個名為 Samsung Galaxy Note7_1097 的 Wifi 訊號，機長立即作出廣播並要求搜查全機乘客的行李去找出呢部「不速之客」。幸好，呢部所謂的 Galaxy Note 7 其實只係其中一位乘客手多多將自己手機的 SSID 改名為 Samsung Galaxy Note7_1097 而已。"},{"pid":"ec0cc3a5b4bfecac75dee9015f3572e79d6c951e","tid":53524,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"如果全機改呢個SSID咪話唔過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c39ec66d5a3d330d986f8c4687ebafbdb65b066","tid":53524,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果全機改呢個SSID咪話唔過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以試下既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}